storu (Hlavní zobrazení)\n    // ==========================================\n\n"]]},{"start1":2810,"length1":34,"diffs":[[1,"     * Přečte přesný náklon robota (Pitch) v ose X pomocí registru V5+.\n     * Vrací úhel od -90.0° (nos dolů) do +90.0° (nos nahoru).\n"]]},{"start1":2953,"length1":51,"diffs":[[1,"    //% block=\"náklon (pitch) z CMPS14 || adresa %addr\"\n"]]},{"start1":3032,"length1":33,"diffs":[[1,"    //% group=\"Poloha v prostoru\"\n"]]},{"start1":3365,"length1":33,"diffs":[[1,"     * Přečte přesné klopení robota (Roll) v ose Y pomocí registru V5+.\n     * Vrací úhel od -180.0° do +180.0°.\n"]]},{"start1":3486,"length1":50,"diffs":[[1,"    //% block=\"klopení (roll) z CMPS14 || adresa %addr\"\n"]]},{"start1":3565,"length1":33,"diffs":[[1,"    //% group=\"Poloha v prostoru\"\n"]]},{"start1":3889,"length1":0,"diffs":[[1,"\n    // ==========================================\n    // SKUPINA: Nastavení (Hlavní zobrazení)\n    // ==========================================\n\n"]]},{"start1":4044,"length1":33,"diffs":[[1,"     * Přečte stav interní kalibrace senzoru (0-255). Hodnota 255 znamená kompletní zkalibrování.\n"]]},{"start1":4150,"length1":64,"diffs":[[1,"    //% block=\"stav kalibrace z CMPS14 || adresa %addr\"\n"]]},{"start1":4229,"length1":25,"diffs":[[1,"    //% group=\"Nastavení\"\n"]]},{"start1":4532,"length1":52,"diffs":[[1,"     * Uloží aktuální kalibrační profil do permanentní paměti senzoru flash.\n"]]},{"start1":4617,"length1":68,"diffs":[[1,"    //% block=\"uložit kalibrační profil do flash || adresa %addr\"\n"]]},{"start1":4706,"length1":25,"diffs":[[1,"    //% group=\"Nastavení\"\n"]]},{"start1":5179,"length1":28,"diffs":[[1,"     * Změní I2C adresu senzoru ze staré adresy na novou. \n     * Na sběrnici musí být připojen pouze JEDEN senzor! Povolené adresy jsou 0xC0, 0xC2, 0xC4 atd.\n"]]},{"start1":5346,"length1":61,"diffs":[[1,"    //% block=\"změnit I2C adresu z %oldAddr na %newAddr\"\n"]]},{"start1":5447,"length1":25,"diffs":[[1,"    //% group=\"Nastavení\"\n"]]},{"start1":6047,"length1":263,"diffs":[[1,""]]},{"start1":6048,"length1":238,"diffs":[[1,"    // ==========================================\n    // SEKCE \"VÍC...\" (ADVANCED) + JEDNOTLIVÉ SKUPINY\n    // ==========================================\n"]]},{"start1":6203,"length1":214,"diffs":[[1,"    // --- MAGNETOMETR ---\n    /**\n     * Surová hodnota z magnetometru v ose X.\n     */\n    //% block=\"magnetometr osa X || adresa %addr\"\n    //% addr.defl=0xC0\n    //% group=\"Magnetometr\" advanced=true\n    export function rawMagnetometerX(addr: number = 0xC0): number {\n        let i2cAddr = addr >> 1;\n        pins.i2cWriteNumber(i2cAddr, 0x06, NumberFormat.Int8LE, true);\n        return pins.i2cReadNumber(i2cAddr, NumberFormat.Int16BE, false);\n    }\n\n    //% block=\"magnetometr osa Y || adresa %addr\"\n    //% addr.defl=0xC0\n    //% group=\"Magnetometr\" advanced=true\n    export function rawMagnetometerY(addr: number = 0xC0): number {\n        let i2cAddr = addr >> 1;\n        pins.i2cWriteNumber(i2cAddr, 0x08, NumberFormat.Int8LE, true);\n        return pins.i2cReadNumber(i2cAddr, NumberFormat.Int16BE, false);\n    }\n\n    //% block=\"magnetometr osa Z || adresa %addr\"\n    //% addr.defl=0xC0\n    //% group=\"Magnetometr\" advanced=true\n    export function rawMagnetometerZ(addr: number = 0xC0): number {\n        let i2cAddr = addr >> 1;\n        pins.i2cWriteNumber(i2cAddr, 0x0A, NumberFormat.Int8LE, true);\n        return pins.i2cReadNumber(i2cAddr, NumberFormat.Int16BE, false);\n    }\n\n    // --- AKCELEROMETR ---\n    /**\n     * Zrychlení v ose X očištěné o gravitaci (v m/s²).\n     */\n    //% block=\"akcelerometr osa X (m/s²) || adresa %addr\"\n    //% addr.defl=0xC0\n    //% group=\"Akcelerometr\" advanced=true\n    export function accelerationX(addr: number = 0xC0): number {\n        let i2cAddr = addr >> 1;\n        pins.i2cWriteNumber(i2cAddr, 0x0C, NumberFormat.Int8LE, true);\n        let raw = pins.i2cReadNumber(i2cAddr, NumberFormat.Int16BE, false);\n        return raw / 256;\n    }\n\n    //% block=\"akcelerometr osa Y (m/s²) || adresa %addr\"\n    //% addr.defl=0xC0\n    //% group=\"Akcelerometr\" advanced=true\n    export function accelerationY(addr: number = 0xC0): number {\n        let i2cAddr = addr >> 1;\n        pins.i2cWriteNumber(i2cAddr, 0x0E, NumberFormat.Int8LE, true);\n        let raw = pins.i2cReadNumber(i2cAddr, NumberFormat.Int16BE, false);\n        return raw / 256;\n    }\n\n    //% block=\"akcelerometr osa Z (m/s²) || adresa %addr\"\n    //% addr.defl=0xC0\n    //% group=\"Akcelerometr\" advanced=true\n    export function accelerationZ(addr: number = 0xC0): number {\n        let i2cAddr = addr >> 1;\n        pins.i2cWriteNumber(i2cAddr, 0x10, NumberFormat.Int8LE, true);\n        let raw = pins.i2cReadNumber(i2cAddr, NumberFormat.Int16BE, false);\n        return raw / 256;\n    }\n\n    // --- GYROSKOP ---\n    /**\n     * Surová hodnota rychlosti rotace z gyroskopu (osa X).\n     */\n    //% block=\"gyroskop osa X || adresa %addr\"\n    //% addr.defl=0xC0\n    //% group=\"Gyroskop\" advanced=true\n    export function rawGyroX(addr: number = 0xC0): number {\n        let i2cAddr = addr >> 1;\n        pins.i2cWriteNumber(i2cAddr, 0x12, NumberFormat.Int8LE, true);\n        return pins.i2cReadNumber(i2cAddr, NumberFormat.Int16BE, false);\n    }\n\n    //% block=\"gyroskop osa Y || adresa %addr\"\n    //% addr.defl=0xC0\n    //% group=\"Gyroskop\" advanced=true\n    export function rawGyroY(addr: number = 0xC0): number {\n        let i2cAddr = addr >> 1;\n        pins.i2cWriteNumber(i2cAddr, 0x14, NumberFormat.Int8LE, true);\n        return pins.i2cReadNumber(i2cAddr, NumberFormat.Int16BE, false);\n    }\n\n    //% block=\"gyroskop osa Z || adresa %addr\"\n    //% addr.defl=0xC0\n    //% group=\"Gyroskop\" advanced=true\n    export function rawGyroZ(addr: number = 0xC0): number {\n        let i2cAddr = addr >> 1;\n        pins.i2cWriteNumber(i2cAddr, 0x16, NumberFormat.Int8LE, true);\n        return pins.i2cReadNumber(i2cAddr, NumberFormat.Int16BE, false);\n    }\n"]]}]}]},{"timestamp":1779212834049,"editorVersion":"8.0.22","changes":[{"type":"edited","filename":"main.blocks","patch":[{"start1":0,"length1":714,"diffs":[[1,"<xml xmlns=\"https://developers.google.com/blockly/xml\"><variables></variables><block type=\"device_forever\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"><statement name=\"HANDLER\"><block type=\"device_show_number\"><value name=\"number\"><shadow type=\"math_number\"><field name=\"NUM\">0</field></shadow><block type=\"CMPS14_readAzimuth\"><mutation xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" _expanded=\"0\" _input_init=\"true\"></mutation><field name=\"precision\">CMPS14_Precision.Degrees</field><value name=\"addr\"><shadow type=\"math_number\"><field name=\"NUM\">192</field></shadow></value></block></value></block></statement></block></xml>"]]}]},{"type":"edited","filename":"main.ts","patch":[{"start1":28,"length1":67,"diffs":[[1,"    basic.showNumber(CMPS14.readAzimuth())\n"]]}]},{"type":"edited","filename":"pxt.json","patch":[{"start1":250,"length1":75,"diffs":[[1,"    \"preferredEditor\": \"blocksprj\"\n"]]}]},{"type":"edited","filename":"cmps14.ts","patch":[{"start1":511,"length1":79,"diffs":[[1,"    //% block=\"azimuth from CMPS14 || with precision %precision address %addr\"\n"]]},{"start1":1472,"length1":102,"diffs":[[1,"    //% block=\"heading deviation to target %targetHeading || with precision %precision address %addr\"\n"]]},{"start1":4129,"length1":29,"diffs":[[1,"     * Changes I2C address.\n"]]}]},{"type":"added","filename":"test.ts","value":"// tests go here; this will not be compiled when this package is used as an extension.\n"}]}],"snapshots":[{"timestamp":1779197149880,"editorVersion":"8.0.22","text":{"main.blocks":"<xml xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n  <block type=\"pxt-on-start\"></block>\n  <block type=\"device_forever\"></block>\n</xml>","main.ts":"\n","README.md":"","pxt.json":"{\n    \"name\": \"c